sentences.english: Serial. println() just prints a carriage return and a linefeed .

sentences.english: So I run this, Enter, and therein lies the nothing.
sentences.chinese: 我運行它，回車，但那裏什麼也沒出現。

sentences.english: For text-mode files, carriage return–linefeed pairs are counted as single characters.
